Label: STR_7_53C
English:
"Bugsite" is a world inside the Internet, divided into four places.
"Ami Land", from land company FE, "Sea Land" from sea company Sting, "Air Land" from air company Ruger, and "Energy Land" from power company Tahiro.
Since Techno Area is part of Ami Land, FE maintains jurisdiction over it.

Label: STR_7_54D
Notes:
(This sounds a little literal, but it's also correct.
Later dialogue states that FE has control over "land-based computers", and so on and so forth, so we're going with "land company", "sea company" etc.)
